main event: A report was filed regarding a UFO sighting in Roseburg, Oregon on November 13, 1961.
interesting points: The report includes a file number (772N) specific to the sighting., Two photographs are included in the document., The first photo depicts a landscape with a hilly background and trees., The second photo shows a rural setting with buildings and fences but no visible UFOs or human subjects., The report is marked as unclassified by the Foreign Technology Division, AFSC.
